00:54:38,269 --> 00:54:40,620
Don't say another word!

527
00:54:41,430 --> 00:54:44,708
There's something about Goo Joon Pyo that I know and you don't.

528
00:54:44,708 --> 00:54:50,014
No, I know. You're the one that doesn't know.

529
00:54:50,014 --> 00:54:51,682
Why are you doing this?

530
00:54:51,682 --> 00:54:57,087
Way before you even met him, I've known the kind of person he is.

531
00:54:57,087 --> 00:55:00,280
With the exception of F4, he doesn't see people as people.

532
00:55:00,280 --> 00:55:04,160
He sees the lives and happiness of other people as something as insignificant as an insect.

533
00:55:04,160 --> 00:55:05,990
No,

534
00:55:06,710 --> 00:55:10,630
he used to be like that, but not now.

535
00:55:10,630 --> 00:55:14,441
That's not all there is to Goo Joon Pyo.

536
00:55:16,640 --> 00:55:18,909
Once you get to know him—

537
00:55:21,770 --> 00:55:23,513
Give up.

538
00:55:24,710 --> 00:55:29,419
From the beginning, you and him weren't meant to be.

539
00:55:30,150 --> 00:55:32,420
Be with me.

540
00:55:32,420 --> 00:55:34,610
Don't we get along?

541
00:55:35,191 --> 00:55:39,930
Sunbae, aren't we of the same world?

542
00:55:46,900 --> 00:55:51,410
We were only friends. You were someone I was really thankful for,

543
00:55:51,410 --> 00:55:53,300
but...

544
00:55:54,740 --> 00:55:55,779
I can't.

545
00:55:55,779 --> 00:55:59,030
No way. Do you still trust him?

546
00:55:59,030 --> 00:56:01,151
After all the things that he's done to you?

547
00:56:01,151 --> 00:56:03,053
I do.

548
00:56:04,320 --> 00:56:05,889
I trust him.

549
00:56:05,889 --> 00:56:07,790
Because...

550
00:56:09,640 --> 00:56:12,228
Goo Joon Pyo trusted me.

551
00:56:12,228 --> 00:56:14,497
Because Goo Joon Pyo would trust in me.

552
00:56:29,980 --> 00:56:32,060
You'll regret this.

553
00:56:33,450 --> 00:56:34,851
Wake up already!

554
00:56:34,851 --> 00:56:37,980
I'm more awake now than I've ever been before.

555
00:56:37,980 --> 00:56:41,530
I know what I did wrong

556
00:56:41,530 --> 00:56:44,460
and what Goo Joon Pyo means to me now.

557
00:56:46,860 --> 00:56:48,698
I'll be leaving now.

558
00:56:56,670 --> 00:57:00,870
Je Ha's world, Joon Pyo's world,

559
00:57:00,870 --> 00:57:03,310
there's no difference.

560
00:57:04,670 --> 00:57:08,510
If they exist in the same place and are surrounded by the same things,

561
00:57:09,230 --> 00:57:11,450
then there's no difference.

562
00:57:33,100 --> 00:57:38,014
I warned you that you'd regret this.

563
00:57:48,660 --> 00:57:50,193
Young Master.

564
00:57:50,193 --> 00:57:52,520
You haven't called.

565
00:57:52,520 --> 00:57:55,360
