566
00:57:55,362 --> 00:57:56,800
Why should they be worried about me?

567
00:57:56,800 --> 00:58:01,070
It's not about that. It's about Miss Geum Jan Di.

568
00:58:01,070 --> 00:58:03,540
Jan Di? What happened to Jan Di?

569
00:58:03,540 --> 00:58:06,143
I don't know the details.

570
00:58:08,490 --> 00:58:11,314
Here is a letter for you.

571
00:58:16,620 --> 00:58:19,022
[If you want to save Geum Jan Di, come alone.]

572
00:58:22,100 --> 00:58:27,040
