574
00:58:43,810 --> 00:58:45,740
It's nothing.

575
00:58:46,440 --> 00:58:49,019
Butler Lee, I'm a little tired so I think I'm going to go upstairs and sleep.

576
00:58:49,019 --> 00:58:50,854
At this time?

577
00:58:50,854 --> 00:58:53,356
Tell everyone not to bother me.

578
00:58:55,050 --> 00:58:57,360
Why am I so tired?

579
00:59:31,020 --> 00:59:32,563
Joon Pyo came in, right? Is he in his room?

580
00:59:32,563 --> 00:59:35,297
Young master said... Uh, young masters.

581
00:59:35,297 --> 00:59:39,050
Don't worry. Even if he makes a fuss, we'll take care of it.

582
00:59:39,700 --> 00:59:43,405
Joon Pyo. Goo Joon Pyo!

583
00:59:43,405 --> 00:59:46,590
- Joon Pyo.
- Joon Pyo, get up!

584
00:59:46,590 --> 00:59:48,740
Are you really going to act like this?

585
00:59:54,480 --> 00:59:56,386
Something is wrong.

586
00:59:59,990 --> 01:00:02,580
Joon Pyo! Joon Pyo!

587
01:00:02,580 --> 01:00:04,240
Joon Pyo!

588
01:00:06,920 --> 01:00:09,665
Guys, over here.

589
01:00:17,840 --> 01:00:20,770
As soon as he came back, there was a weird letter.

590
01:00:20,770 --> 01:00:22,540
Letter?

591
01:00:48,960 --> 01:00:51,340
Guys, go out and check if he's coming.

592
01:01:01,380 --> 01:01:03,787
Your eyes tell me you have a lot to say,

593
01:01:03,787 --> 01:01:05,771
Jan Di Sunbae.

594
01:01:26,140 --> 01:01:28,130
What's your true identity?

595
01:01:28,640 --> 01:01:30,613
Why are you doing this?

596
01:01:30,613 --> 01:01:32,748
I have a reason.

597
01:01:33,580 --> 01:01:35,618
Two reasons.

598
01:01:35,618 --> 01:01:36,853
Two?

599
01:01:36,853 --> 01:01:42,439
The incidents at the part-time job, the red card, and the classroom.

600
01:01:43,620 --> 01:01:46,028
They were all done by me.

601
01:01:46,028 --> 01:01:48,197
You didn't know they were me, right?

602
01:01:51,330 --> 01:01:53,170
Jan Di Sunbae.

603
01:01:54,030 --> 01:01:56,105
Look closely.

604
01:01:57,700 --> 01:01:59,442
Do I look like someone

605
01:02:00,410 --> 01:02:02,712
