619
01:03:00,250 --> 01:03:02,310
Ga Eul! Ga Eul, be careful!

620
01:03:02,310 --> 01:03:05,570
Ga Eul, are you okay? Wake up.

621
01:03:05,570 --> 01:03:08,470
I'm sorry, I was definitely wearing it on my neck...

622
01:03:08,470 --> 01:03:10,520
You're always like this.

623
01:03:10,520 --> 01:03:15,940
Whenever I approach you genuinely, you treat my feelings lightly.

624
01:03:15,940 --> 01:03:18,560
We're in trouble. Jan Di went to the mountains...

625
01:03:18,560 --> 01:03:20,140
Where is Joon Pyo right now?

626
01:03:20,140 --> 01:03:24,370
